    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This mid-engine 3.4L flat-six powerhouse features VarioCam Plus for an optimized torque curve, delivering linear power delivery to a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, featuring a MacPherson strut suspension layout that provides exceptional lateral stability and communicative hydraulic steering. Recent preventative maintenance includes a cooling system refresh and a comprehensive bore-scope inspection to ensure the integrity of the cylinder walls. Equipped with four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors, the braking system offers consistent thermal management and firm pedal feel, making this a mechanically sound example for the discerning driver.",
